# cfv

Calculate and verify file checksums recursively on directory tree

## Usage

Usage: `cfv [OPTIONS] DIR [DIR2 ...]`

### Options

`-a b3|md5|sha256|sha512`	Select hash algorithms. Default: `b3`
`-c`				Check existing checksums instead of creating those (which is default)
`-u`				Update missing checksums
`-U`				Check and update existing checksums
`-A`				Create a summary file with all the checksums in addition to the per directory checksum files. 
